Subject: [PATCH] staging: vchiq_core: Free kthreads in error case
Git-commit: a69b41e90aedbfd04dc34d3e0df96143d99ab71b
Patch-mainline: v4.18-rc1
References: FATE#324827

We need to free the kthreads in error case before leaving
vchiq_init_state() otherwise we leak resources.

Signed-off-by: Stefan Wahren <stefan.wahren@i2se.com>
Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

